<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-astonishing">1.★ <strong>令人惊异的(astonishing)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is really amazing that the once-ruined place has now been turned into a beautiful school.
曾被摧毁的地方现在已变成了一所美丽的学校，真让人难以相信。</p><footer>2011福建</footer></div></div>